&lt;h3 id="make_heap"&gt;make_heap&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;make heap from range&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We need to have a heap before we operate on a heap, &lt;code&gt;make_heap&lt;/code&gt; let&amp;rsquo;s us rearrange elements in a range.&lt;/p&gt;</description><dc:creator>&lt;a href="https://sky-bro.github.io" class="theme-link"&gt;Kyle&lt;/a&gt;</dc:creator><category>C++</category><category>heap</category><category>map[categories:[Data Structure &amp; Algorithm] image:images/icons/stack of rocks.png]</category></item></channel></rss>